<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 09:16:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国将欧盟乳制品调查范围扩大到更多补贴计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-widens-eu-dairy-probe-more-subsidy-programmes-2024-11-22/</link><description>中国周五扩大了对从欧盟进口乳制品的反补贴调查，调查范围包括欧盟以及丹麦、法国、意大利和荷兰的补贴计划。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 08:47:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-widens-eu-dairy-probe-more-subsidy-programmes-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金 随着价格反弹，印度和其他亚洲中心的黄金需求不温不火</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-gold-demand-tepid-india-other-asian-hubs-prices-rebound-2024-11-22/</link><description>印度实物黄金溢价本周因需求回落而下滑，原因是当地价格上涨促使珠宝商和零售买家保持观望，而最大消费国中国和其他主要亚洲中心对黄金的需求也依然低迷。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 08:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-gold-demand-tepid-india-other-asian-hubs-prices-rebound-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国扩大对日本、保加利亚等国免签待遇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-expands-visa-free-access-japan-bulgaria-other-countries-2024-11-22/</link><description>外交部发言人周五表示，中国将扩大免签安排范围，将日本、保加利亚、罗马尼亚、克罗地亚、黑山等国家纳入其中，自2024年11月30日至2025年12月31日生效。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-expands-visa-free-access-japan-bulgaria-other-countries-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>德克萨斯州州长命令州机构出售中国资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/texas-governor-orders-state-agencies-divest-china-assets-2024-11-22/</link><description>德克萨斯州州长以金融和安全风险为由，下令各州机构停止在中国的投资并尽快出售在中国的资产，这是中美紧张局势升级开始影响全球资本流动的迹象。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 07:36:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/texas-governor-orders-state-agencies-divest-china-assets-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>BP与合作伙伴将投资70亿美元在印度尼西亚巴布亚建设碳捕集项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/bp-partners-invest-7-billion-carbon-capture-project-indonesias-papua-2024-11-22/</link><description>英国石油公司及其合作伙伴表示，他们将投资 70 亿美元用于印度尼西亚最东部巴布亚地区的碳捕集项目和气田开发，这可能会释放 3 万亿立方英尺的额外天然气资源。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 03:27:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/bp-partners-invest-7-billion-carbon-capture-project-indonesias-papua-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>参议员称，美国电信遭受疑似与中国有关的黑客攻击，这是该国历史上最严重的一次</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/suspected-china-linked-hack-us-telecoms-worst-nations-history-senator-says-2024-11-22/</link><description>美国参议院情报委员会主席周四对《华盛顿邮报》表示，美国称与中国有关的电信公司遭受的黑客攻击是“我们国家历史上迄今为止最严重的电信黑客攻击”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 03:11:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/suspected-china-linked-hack-us-telecoms-worst-nations-history-senator-says-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>中方表示愿与美方对话推动双边贸易发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-stable-trade-business-development-with-us-will-benefit-both-nations-2024-11-22/</link><description>商务部副部长王受文周五表示，中方愿在相互尊重的原则基础上与美方积极对话，推动双边经贸关系发展。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-stable-trade-business-development-with-us-will-benefit-both-nations-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>更广泛的乌克兰战争担忧导致金价飙升；科技股反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-22/</link><description>由于地缘政治紧张局势升级促使投资者转向安全资产，周五金价有望创下 13 个月以来的最大单周涨幅，而在对 Nvidia 销售增长的担忧缓解后，科技股反弹导致亚洲股市走高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统将访问图瓦卢、帕劳和马绍尔群岛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-tuvalu-palau-marshall-islands-2024-11-22/</link><description>总统府周五表示，台湾总统赖清德将访问太平洋的图瓦卢、帕劳和马绍尔群岛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:25:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-tuvalu-palau-marshall-islands-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>由于乌克兰战争加剧的焦虑，油价每周上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-intensifying-ukraine-war-increases-supply-risk-2024-11-22/</link><description>随着乌克兰战争愈演愈烈，俄罗斯总统普京警告全球冲突，油价周五小幅走高，有望每周上涨 4% 以上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 02:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-intensifying-ukraine-war-increases-supply-risk-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统将访问太平洋盟友，但没有美国过境的详细信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-pacific-island-nation-allies-2024-11-22/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德办公室周五表示，台湾总统赖清德将从本月底开始访问台北在太平洋地区仅存的三个外交盟友，但政府拒绝透露美国过境地点的详细信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-president-visit-pacific-island-nation-allies-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>习近平访问摩洛哥并会见王储</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-visits-morocco-meets-with-crown-prince-says-state-media-2024-11-22/</link><description>据两国官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平周四对摩洛哥进行了短暂访问。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 00:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-visits-morocco-meets-with-crown-prince-says-state-media-2024-11-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易紧张局势加剧，中国企业寻求美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/corporate-china-seeks-dollars-trade-tensions-rise-2024-11-21/</link><description>由于贸易紧张局势可能会扰乱外汇汇率，中国企业正在储备更多美元，以人民币定价合同，并开放进口额度，以减轻货币风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 23:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/corporate-china-seeks-dollars-trade-tensions-rise-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：韧性是游戏的名称，关注日本 CPI</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-21/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构理事会通过伊朗决议，西方推动德黑兰进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-nuclear-watchdogs-35-nation-board-passes-resolution-against-iran-2024-11-21/</link><description>目的是迫使伊朗就对其核活动的新限制进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 21:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/un-nuclear-watchdogs-35-nation-board-passes-resolution-against-iran-2024-11-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>